   268→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-internet"></div>인터넷망</div>
   269→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-intranet"></div>업무망</div>
   270→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-backup"></div>백업망 (광주)</div>
   271→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-rpm"></div>RPM 직접설치</div>
   272→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-docker"></div>Docker 컨테이너</div>
   273→  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot dot-jar"></div>Spring Boot JAR</div>
   274→</div>
   275→
   276→<div class="main-wrap">
   277→
   278→  <!-- ══ HQ ══ -->
   279→  <div class="section sec-hq">
   280→    <div class="sec-label">HQ — 내부망 (신규)</div>
   281→    <div class="hq-inner">
   282→      <div class="hq-git">
   283→        <h3>📁 Git 저장소 + Ansible GitOps</h3>
   284→        <div class="mono">
   285→          ansible/<br>
   286→          &nbsp;&nbsp;├── roles/ &nbsp;grafana / prometheus / loki / ollama / fastapi / n8n / alloy<br>
   287→          &nbsp;&nbsp;├── profiles/ &nbsp;<span class="hl">bare-metal-highspec.yml</span> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span class="hl">bare-metal-lowspec.yml</span><br>
   288→          &nbsp;&nbsp;└── sites/ &nbsp;<span class="hl">template/</span> &nbsp;/&nbsp; new-safe/ &nbsp;/&nbsp; site-B/
   289→        </div>
   290→      </div>
   291→      <div class="hq-cards">
   292→        <div class="hq-card">
   293→          <h4>⚙️ Ansible Control Node</h4>
   294→          <p>VPN → 현장 배포·설정 변경<br>preflight → deploy → rollback</p>
   295→        </div>
   296→        <div class="hq-card">
   297→          <h4>📡 Health Beacon 집계</h4>
   298→          <p><span class="badge b-gray">v1: 선택</span> &nbsp;<span class="badge b-green">v2: 표준</span></p>
   299→        </div>
   300→      </div>
   301→    </div>
   302→  </div>
